ABAZIBIZA ngomakade bebona kwezempi bangene ngodli ezindlini zomxhaso eKuils River, eKapa. Bathe bangangena bathi sekufike isikhathi lezi zindlu zabelwe abantu ngokukangachemi. Abangu-50 kubona bathe babeyibambe kwi-Azanian People’s Liberation Army (Apla), okwakuwuphiko lwezempi lwePAC. Baqale ukungena kulezi zindlu ngoLwesithathu. Baphinde balandelwa abanye abazibiza ngeSA Coloured Corps (SACC) Military Veterans. Unobhala wabo uMnuz Billiard Zwelizolile Seth, uthe bazohlala kulezi zindlu baze banikezwe ezabo. “Lezi zindlu ezabalweli benkululeko. Kumele nathi sibhekelelwe,” kusho uSeth. Uthe lokhu bakwenzela ukuthi bahlale nemindeni yabo. Emhlanganweni ababe nawo nomele uMnyango wezokuHlaliswa kwaBantu ngoLwesine, abazange baneliswe abatshelwa kona. Uthe sekunesikhathi eside uhulumeni enikezwe isikhathi sokuthi alungise lolu daba kodwa angalusukumeli, kunalokho babenzele phansi. Okhulumela iSACC uMnuz Ronald Plaatjies, uthe bazimisele ngokusebenzisana njengoba sebehlala kule ndawo ukuze omakadebona nabo babelwe izindlu ngendlela enobulungiswa. Okhulumela uMnyango wezokuHlaliswa kwaBantu kulesiya sifundazwe, uNksz Muneera Allie, uthe izinhlaka zomthetho zikhona kuleya ndawo ukubhekela ukuthi isimo sihamba ngokuyikho, okuwukugwema ukuthi abekho abangena ezindlini ngokungemthetho. ‘‘Le ndawo isathuthukiswa. UMnyango uyakuqikelela ukuthi kuhlale kunokuphepha nezempilo ezisezingeni elifanele ezihlelwayo esimeni esifana naleso,” kusho * -Allie. Uthe uma kukhona abangene ngokungemthetho bazokhishwa uma kungukuthi abaziphumeli ngokwabo. Uthe nakuba kunjalo, kuyiqiniso ukuthi lezi zindlu zihlinzekelwe omakadebona bezempi okukhona kubo namalungu e-Apla.